{"article_id":"DKz9dSllHJePRqgL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"With no clear path forward","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to derail Judge Brett Kavanaugh 's nomination to the Supreme Court ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"liberal activists in Maine have resorted to questionable tactics","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"to urge moderate , pro-choice Republican Sen. Susan Collins","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"( R-ME )","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to vote against the nominee .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Both the Maine People 's Alliance and Mainers for Accountable Leadership joined forces","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and set up a crowdfunding site","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that has raised over $ 1 million .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"According to the website ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"there are two scenarios :","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"`` Sen. Collins votes NO on Kavanaugh","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"and you will not be charged ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and no money will go to fund her future opponent . ''","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"`` Sen. Collins votes YES on Kavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"and your pledge will go to her opponent 's campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"once that opponent has been identified . ''","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"The website goes on to threaten","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"if she votes in favor of his nomination ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"`` We will get you out of office . ''","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"`` Your swing vote could decide","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"whether a rubber stamp for Trump 's anti-healthcare , anti-woman , anti-labor agenda gets confirmed to the Supreme Court-costing millions of Americans their health care , their right","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"to choose","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"and their lives , ''","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"the website continues .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"In a statement to Newsmax , Sen. Collins said","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"their efforts `` will not influence my vote at all . ''","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"`` I consider this quid pro quo fundraising to be the equivalent of an attempt","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"to bribe me","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"to vote against Judge Kavanaugh , ''","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"Collins told Newsmax .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"it demonstrates the new lows","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"to which the judge 's opponents have stooped . ''","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Throughout the ongoing confirmation process , activists have sent over 3,000 wire hangers to the senator 's office .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"And NBC 's Kasie Hunt told `` Morning Joe '' Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"that Collins `` had one 25-year-old female staffer have somebody walk up to them","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"and say","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"that they hope","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"that she is raped and impregnated .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"And I 've gotten notes from sources","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"that people feel really uncomfortable with how this is playing out . ''","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Sen. Orrin Hatch","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"( R-UT )","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"took to Twitter","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"to call on Democrats to condemn `` attempts to bribe '' Sen. Collins .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Every Democrat should be condemning these antics in Maine-","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"attempting to bribe Senator Collins","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"to vote against Judge Kavanaugh","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"and threatening sexual violence against staffers","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"if she votes for him","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"is absolutely disgusting .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"https : //t.co/zZ4BEz1PIn","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"- Senator Hatch Office","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"( @ senorrinhatch )","depth":9